---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const pageTitle = "The Best VA Services For Your Business";
const pageDescription = "As a business owner, your time is valuable. Why get bogged down with routine tasks when you could focus on growth and innovation?";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <div class="pt-20 bg-white min-h-screen">
    <div class="w-full px-8 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="mb-8">
              <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">
                The Best VA Services For Your Business
              </h1>
              <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-orange-500 mt-4"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg mb-8">
              <img
                src="/images/resources-page/The Best VA Services For Your Business.webp"
                alt="The Best VA Services For Your Business"
                class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
              <div class="relative w-full" style="padding-bottom: 56.25%; background: #000; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <div class="text-center text-white">
                    <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Video unavailable</p>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-75 mt-2">This video is private</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8">
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                As a business owner, your time is valuable. Why get bogged down with routine tasks when you could focus on growth and innovation? Virtual assistants (VAs) offer an efficient solution, handling tasks like scheduling, email management, and social media, so you can concentrate on what really matters.
              </p>

              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Finding the Right VA Service</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                With numerous VA platforms available, finding remote help has never been easier. Skip the headaches of onboarding and payrollâ€”most services offer a simple, flat-rate model, taking care of everything from HR to taxes.
              </p>

              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Types of VA Support</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">Whether you need:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Administrative support</li>
                <li>Marketing expertise</li>
                <li>Customer service</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                There's a VA service that fits your needs. We've reviewed the top platforms to help you find the perfect match for your business.
              </p>

              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Virtual assistants can transform how you work, giving you back precious time to focus on strategic growth while ensuring day-to-day operations run smoothly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="sticky top-24">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
                <img
                  src="/images/resources-page/The Best VA Services For Your Business.webp"
                  alt="The Best VA Services For Your Business"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg mb-4"
                />
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <a href="/best-va-services/" class="block group">
                  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                      <img
                        src="/images/resources-page/The Best VA Services For Your Business.webp"
                        alt="Best VA Services"
                        class="w-20 h-20 object-cover rounded"
                      />
                      <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors text-[22px]">
                          The Best VA Services For Your Business
                        </h3>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </a>

                <a href="/how-companies-get-their-sht-together/" class="block group">
                  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                      <img
                        src="/images/resources-page/the-system-how-companies-get-their-shit-together.jpg"
                        alt="How companies get their sh*t together"
                        class="w-20 h-20 object-cover rounded"
                      />
